## Legal Compliance Disclaimer

This software is provided "as is" for self-hosting purposes. Users are solely
responsible for ensuring compliance with applicable laws and regulations in
their jurisdiction.

### Export Controls & Sanctions

This software includes encryption capabilities. Users are responsible for:
- Complying with applicable export control laws in their jurisdiction
- Ensuring compliance with sanctions and embargo regulations
- Not using this software in sanctioned or restricted jurisdictions

This software may not be exported or re-exported to persons or entities
blocked, denied, or designated under applicable export control laws.

### Data Protection & Privacy

This software processes personal data (usernames, voice data, messages).
Deployers are responsible for:
- Obtaining necessary consents
- Implementing appropriate data protection measures
- Responding to data subject requests
- Complying with applicable data breach notification requirements

### Telecom & Voice Regulations

This software enables real-time voice communication. Users/deployers are
responsible for:
- Complying with local VoIP/telecom regulations
- Implementing emergency services (e.g., E911) where required
- Lawful interception capabilities where legally mandated
- Any licensing or registration requirements for voice services

